{
  "name": "IconSetCondition",
  "summary": "<p>所有条件格式对象均包含在 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.FormatConditions\">FormatConditions</a></strong> 集合对象中，该集合对象是 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 集合的子项。您可以使用 <strong>FormatConditions</strong> 集合的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.Add\">Add</a></strong> 方法或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.AddIconSetCondition\">AddIconSetCondition</a></strong> 方法创建图标集格式规则。</p>\n<p>每个图标集包含三个、四个或五个图标。您可以使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.Workbook\">Workbook</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.IconSets\">IconSets</a></strong> 属性返回 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconSets/IconSets .htm#IconSets.IconSets\">IconSets</a></strong> 对象以指定其中一个内置图标集。然后按 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconCriteria/IconCriteria .htm#IconCriteria.IconCriteria\">IconCriteria</a></strong> 对象的成员将图标集中每个单独的图标分配给范围中的值的子集。阈值的类型也是由此对象指定的。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建了一个代表测试分数的数字范围，然后对该范围应用了图标集条件格式规则。图标集的类型将从默认图标变为五箭头图标集。最后，将阈值类型从百分点修改为硬编码数字。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Fill cells with sample data from 1 to 10</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">55</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">92</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">88</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">77</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">66</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">93</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C7&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">76</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C8&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C9&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">79</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">83</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C11&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">66</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C12&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">74</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C12&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Create an icon set conditional format for the created sample data range</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddIconSetCondition</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Change the icon set to a five-arrow icon set</span>\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconSets</span>(xl5Arrows)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//The IconCriterion collection contains all IconCriteria</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//By indexing into the collection you can modify each criterion</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion1 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconCriteria</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconCriterion1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriterion1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    iconCriterion1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion2 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconCriteria</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconCriterion2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriterion2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">60</span>\n    iconCriterion2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion3 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconCriteria</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    iconCriterion3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriterion3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">70</span>\n    iconCriterion3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion4 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconCriteria</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    iconCriterion4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriterion4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span>\n    iconCriterion4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion5 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconCriteria</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>)\n    iconCriterion5.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriterion5.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>\n    iconCriterion5.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个图标集条件格式使用的图标集的名称为xl3Arrows，则修改该条件格式所应用于的单元格区域，并将该图标集条件格式设置为仅展示图标。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ID</span> == xl3Arrows) {\n        iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>))\n        iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShowIconOnly</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表图标集条件格式规则。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "AppliesTo",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象，指定格式规则将应用于的单元格区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式应用到的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AppliesTo</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例选中工作表 Sheet1 上区域 A1:A10 中第二个图标集条件格式应用到的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AppliesTo</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "IconCriteria",
      "summary": "<p>在您具有 <strong>IconCriteria</strong> 集合之后，可以使用该集合的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconCriteria/IconCriteria .htm#IconCriteria.Item\">Item</a></strong> 属性返回 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconCriterion/IconCriterion .htm#IconCriterion.IconCriterion\">IconCriterion</a></strong> 对象。<strong>IconCriterion</strong> 对象代表图标集的单个条件。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconCriteria/IconCriteria .htm#IconCriteria.IconCriteria\">IconCriteria</a></strong> 集合，该集合代表图标集条件格式规则的一组条件。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第一个IconCriterion的类型是否为xlConditionValuePercent。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValuePercent)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第二个图标集条件格式的第二个IconCriterion的图标为xlIconYellowExclamation。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Icon</span> = xlIconYellowExclamation\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "IconCriteria",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "IconSet",
      "summary": "<p>通过使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.Workbook\">Workbook</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.IconSets\">IconSets</a></strong> 属性，您可以指定图标集。例如，<code>Selection.FormatConditions(1).IconSet = ActiveWorkbook.IconSets(xl3TrafficLights1)</code> 将对条件格式应用由三个交通信号灯图标组成的图标集。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconSets/IconSets .htm#IconSets.IconSets\">IconSets</a></strong> 集合，该集合指定用于条件格式的图标集。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第二个图标集条件格式使用的图标集的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 B1:B10 中第一个图标集条件格式使用的图标集的名称是否为xl3Flags。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ID</span> == xl3Flags)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PercentileValues",
      "summary": "<p>如果未将每个阈值设置为百分点，则此属性将返回 <strong>False</strong>。如果将此属性设置为 <strong>True</strong>，则会将每个阈值类型设置为百分点。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，该值指明是否使用百分点确定图标集条件格式的阈值。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上单元格区域 B1:B10 的第一个图标集条件格式是否使用百分点确定阈值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PercentileValues</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格区域 B1:B10 的第二个图标集条件格式设置为使用百分点确定阈值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PercentileValues</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Priority",
      "summary": "<p>设置优先级时，值必须为介于 1 和工作表上条件格式规则总数之间的正整数。对于工作表上的所有规则，优先级必须为唯一值，因此，如果更改指定条件格式规则的优先级，将可能会导致工作表上其他规则的优先级值移位。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置条件格式规则的优先级值。当工作表中存在多个条件格式规则时，优先级确定求值的顺序。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个图标集条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第一个图标集条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ReverseOrder",
      "summary": "<p>默认情况下，可以使用的大多数图标集都将使用较多的图像与较大值关联。例如，“三色交通灯”图标集将绿色圆应用于区域上限值，而将红色圆应用于区域的最低值。如果数据的较低值更有意义，如马拉松时间结果，则可能希望反转这些图标应用于区域的次序，使绿色圆与最低值关联。</p>\n<p>如果 <strong>IconSetCondition</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconSetCondition/IconSetCondition .htm#IconSetCondition.IconSet\">IconSet</a></strong> 属性为 <strong>xlCustomSet</strong>，<strong>ReverseOrder</strong> 属性将返回 <strong>False</strong>。此外，如果在 <strong>IconSetCondition</strong> 对象的 <strong>IconSet</strong> 属性为 <strong>xlCustomSet</strong> 时，尝试将 <strong>ReverseOrder</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>True</strong>，ET 将返回运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，该值指示是否保留图标集的图标次序。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格区域 C1:C10 的第一个图标集条件格式是否保留图标集的图标次序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ReverseOrder</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上单元格区域 C1:C10 的第二个图标集条件格式设置为保留图标集的图标次序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ReverseOrder</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ShowIconOnly",
      "summary": "<p>此属性的默认值为 <strong>False</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，该值指示是否仅显示图标集条件格式的图标。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上单元格区域 C1:C10 的第一个图标集条件格式是否仅展示图标。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShowIconOnly</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格区域 C1:C10 的第二个图标集条件格式设置为仅展示图标。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShowIconOnly</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "StopIfTrue",
      "summary": "<p>为了支持向后兼容性，此属性的默认值为 <strong>True</strong>，而这与在用户界面中创建的格式规则的行为相反。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，该值确定在当前规则的计算结果为 <strong>True</strong> 时是否应计算单元格上的其他格式规则，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第一个图标集条件格式的计算结果为True时是否停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">StopIfTrue</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;条件格式的计算结果为 True 时停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;条件格式的计算结果为 True 时计算单元格上的其他格式规则&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个图标集条件格式设置为当计算结果为True时是否停止计算单元格上的其他格式规则。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">StopIfTrue</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "<p>此属性将始终返回 <strong>Long</strong> 值“6”，等价于 <strong>xlIconSets</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlFormatConditionType 枚举.html\">XlFormatConditionType</a></strong> 枚举的常量之一，该常量指定条件格式的类型。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第一个条件格式的类型是否为图标集。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlIconSets)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一张工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个条件格式的类型是否为图标集，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlIconSets) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;类型为图标集&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;类型不为图标集&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除指定的条件格式规则对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个图标集条件格式仅展示图标，则删除该条件格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShowIconOnly</span>) {\n        iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "ModifyAppliesToRange",
      "summary": "<p>该区域必须采用 A1 引用样式，并全部包含在 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatConditions/FormatConditions .htm#FormatConditions.FormatConditions\">FormatConditions</a></strong> 集合的父工作表内。可包括区域操作符（冒号）、相交区域操作符（空格）或合并区域操作符（逗号）。也可以使用货币符号，但会被忽略。</p>\n<p>您也可以在区域的任意部分中使用局部定义名称，但该名称必须使用宏语言。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>设置此格式规则所应用于的单元格区域。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置第一张工作表上单元格区域 B1:B10 的第二个图标集条件格式所应用于的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B4&quot;</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格区域 B1:B10 的第一个图标集条件格式使用的图标集的名称为xl3Flags，则修改该条件格式所应用于的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ID</span> == xl3Flags) {\n        iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ModifyAppliesToRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B7:B9&quot;</span>))\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Range",
          "type": "Range",
          "description": "<p>此格式规则将应用于的区域。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetFirstPriority",
      "summary": "<p>当工作表中有多个条件格式规则时，如果之前未将此规则设置为优先级“1”，此方法将导致工作表上的所有其他现有规则的优先级都增加 1。</p>\n<p>将在工作表级别应用条件格式规则的优先级。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>将此条件格式规则的优先级值设置为“1”，以便在工作表上的所有其他规则之前计算此规则。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个图标集条件格式的优先级值设置为“1”，然后删除该区域上第一个图标集条件格式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第二个图标集条件格式的优先级设置为“1”，并选中区域 C1:C6 中第一个图标集条件格式的应用到的单元格区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">AppliesTo</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "SetLastPriority",
      "summary": "<p>优先级的实际值将等于工作表上条件格式规则的总数。当工作表中有多个条件格式规则时，此方法将导致优先级值大于此规则的规则的优先级降低 1。</p>\n<p>将在工作表级别应用条件格式规则的优先级。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>为此条件格式规则设置求值顺序，以便在工作表上的所有其他规则之后计算此规则。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上区域 C1:C10 中第二个图标集条件格式的求值顺序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetLastPriority</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 上区域 C1:C10 中第一个图标集条件格式的求值顺序，并显示该条件格式的优先级值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetLastPriority</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}